data.title: where to sleep in Villafranca del Bierzo a famus stage of The Camino Francés
data.meta_description: Villafranca del Bierzo is it’s a stopover point on The Camino Francés and The Camino  Aragonés.  You can reach Fisterra in 11 days and Santiago de Compostela in 8 days.
